<function>

access:   public

name: fetchTags

param: string|array, $where, NULL

return: array

</function>

Fetches a list of all tags on all nodes of this type with a
count of how many each tag occurs.

* Parameters:

 * string|array //$where//: A set of multiWhere() conditions to determine which nodes are fetched.

* Returns array: An array of tags.